        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "id": "340bef17-e035-8099-844a-e9012a4d973b",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "richText": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The roadmap was adopted and 3 PMs are now executing the strategy.",
          "bold": false,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "id": "340bef17-e035-802c-8a4c-e42cb6d26f2a",
      "type": "heading_3",
      "richText": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The Opportunity",
          "bold": true,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "340bef17-e035-8017-8754-f4c92eab044a",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "richText": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Airwallex's core payments infrastructure was powerful but lacked a lightweight no-code entry point for merchants who did not want API integrations. We saw growing demand from education providers, event organizers, and SMBs who needed something simpler in low-dev-resource environments.",
          "bold": false,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "340bef17-e035-80e9-a7c6-daed8ccb96eb",
      "type": "quote",
      "richText": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Build a link-based payment tool that was fast to create, flexible to customize, and trusted by users from day one.",
          "bold": true,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "340bef17-e035-8013-a19b-e893de64a7eb",
      "type": "heading_3",
      "richText": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Understand the problem space",
          "bold": true,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "340bef17-e035-8076-b94c-d2bfb78d7383",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "richText": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "To shape the direction of Payment Link, I partnered with UX to run surveys and interviews across markets. Merchants consistently wanted strong pricing, broad payment method coverage, integration with back-office tools, and flexible customer-facing customization.",
          "bold": false,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "340bef17-e035-8053-919e-dd23ce2f8a69",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "richText": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "While many existing merchants were in Hong Kong and China, needs were highly localized and less aligned with early product capabilities. We identified clearer product-market fit in Australia, especially for e-commerce and professional services, and focused v1 there.",
          "bold": false,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "340bef17-e035-801c-9a2c-f114896ac71b",
      "type": "heading_3",
      "richText": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Define product strategy",
          "bold": true,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "340bef17-e035-8095-bd52-e61ac0b29755",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "richText": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "I spoke with sales, marketing, and operations teams to understand the competitive landscape. Airwallex had a strong cross-border pricing edge, but we were missing key payment methods like AMEX and Discover in English-speaking markets.",
          "bold": false,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "340bef17-e035-80df-a324-e880e9c87fbc",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "richText": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "🚀 ",
          "bold": false,
          "italic": true,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Launch quickly to serve the cross-border use case we could win today.",
          "bold": false,
          "italic": false,
          "strikethrough": false,
          "underline": false,
          "code": false,
          "color": "default",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "id": "340bef17-e035-808f-ae79-d6e6eb0dd814",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "richText": [
        {
          "type": "text",
