      "type": "paragraph",
      "richText": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "To ensure a smooth rollout, I established lightweight processes for cross-functional reviews, decision-making, and launch readiness. Working across time zones, I kept engineering, design, ops, and GTM aligned with clear documentation and async coordination.",
